         under.
        </para>
       </listitem>

       <listitem>
        <para>
         <emphasis>Add REPLICATION privilege for ROLEs</emphasis>
        </para>
        <para>
         This makes it possible for replication to be performed by a
         non-superuser account.
        </para>
       </listitem>

      </itemizedlist>
    </sect3>
