        </para>
       </listitem>

       <listitem>
        <para>
         Add three-parameter forms of array_to_string and
         string_to_array
        </para>
       </listitem>

       <listitem>
        <para>
         Add XMLEXISTS function
        </para>
       </listitem>

       <listitem>
        <para>
         Add xpath_exists() function
        </para>
        <para>
         This is equivalent to XMLEXISTS except that it offers support for
